Larry Brandenburg https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Larry_Brandenburg 0 Larry Brandenburg (born May 3, 1948) is an American actor. He has appeared in numerous television shows and films such as The Shawshank Redemption, Fargo, The Santa Clause and The Untouchables. Larry_Brandenburg ( born May_3_,_1948 ) is an_American_actor .
